datafield.subfield: ECIP title page (Jennifer Wu) data view (nature and landscape photographer and night photographer; received her BA in photography from California State University, Sacramento; has been photographing for more than twenty-six years; Sacramento, California is her home base between travel adventures; she lectures, gives seminars and workshops, and leads tours to regions as varied as Namibia, Death Valley, Greenland, Montana, and Iceland; her images can be seen at www.jenniferwu.com)
